==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Turncoat
<hw>Turn"coat`</hw> <pr>(t⟦ucir⟧rn"k⟦omac⟧t`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>One who forsakes his party or his principles; a renegade; an
apostate; a defector to the enemy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He is a <qex>turncoat</qex>, he was not true to his
profession.</q> <rj><qau>Bunyan.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Turndown</ent>⟦br⟧
